iver-won-36million-shows-up-work-next-monday-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pipe%20To%20Ambulance%20To%20Hospital%3A%20Uttarkashi%20Tunnel%20Rescue%20Plan%2C%20Step%20By%20Step%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20rescue%20teams%2C%20the%20operation%20involved%20drilling%20through%20the%20debris%20to%20push%20wide%20pipes%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%20to%20walk%20out%20through.%20The%20auger%20machine%2C%20which%20drills%20through%20about%203%20metres%20of%20debris%20in%20an%20hour%2C%20had%20hit%20a%20metal%20obstruction%20early%20this%20morning.%20A%20metal%20cutter%20was%20then%20used%20to%20remove%20the%20block%20and%20the%20operation%20resumed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20auger%20machine%20drills%20through%2C%20pipes%20are%20pushed%20through%20the%20debris.%20Once%20a%20pipe%20is%20all%20in%2C%20another%20is%20welded%20to%20it.%20In%20this%20manner%2C%20an%20escape%20route%20is%20being%20prepped%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%20out%20of%20their%20long%20confinement.%C2%A0Welders%20have%20been%20flown%20in%20from%20Delhi%20to%20put%20together%20the%20final%20stretch%20of%20the%20pipe.%20They%20will%20get%20to%20work%20once%20the%20drilling%20ends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20merely%20bringing%20the%20workers%20out%20of%20the%20tunnel%20is%20not%20enough.%20The%2041%20men%20have%20been%20inside%20for%2012%20days%20now%2C%20during%20which%20they%20have%20only%20received%20a%20couple%20of%20proper%20meals.%20The%20temperature%20difference%20between%20the%20tunnel%20and%20outside%20and%20the%20psychological%20impact%20of%20this%20confinement%20on%20the%20workers%20are%20also%20being%20accounted%20for.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnce%20the%20rescue%20pipe%20reaches%20the%20workers%2C%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20would%20go%20and%20check%20their%20condition.%20He%20would%20show%20them%20how%20to%20crawl%20through%20the%20pipes%20that%20have%20sharp%20edges%20at%20welding%20joints.%20Rescue%20teams%20have%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20stretchers%20have%20also%20been%20arranged.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20workers%20will%20walk%20through%20the%20pipe%20under%20close%20supervision%20of%20the%20NDRF.%20Outside%20the%20tunnel%2C%2041%20ambulances%20are%20on%20standby%20to%20take%20the%20workers%20to%20a%20makeshift%20hospital%20that%20has%20come%20up%20in%20Chinyalisour.%20Rescue%20workers%20said%20the%20workers%20would%20go%20through%20a%20detailed%20medical%20examination%20once%20they%20reach%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EForty-four%20pipes%20have%20been%20inserted%20after%20horizontal%20drilling%20so%20far%2C%20rescue%20officer%20Harpal%20Singh%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20found%20steel%20rods%20in%20the%20debris.%20The%20machine%20couldn't%20cut%20those%20rods.%20NDRF%20personnel%20will%20cut%20those%20rods%20and%20use%20the%20machine%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tunnel%2C%20part%20of%20the%20centre's%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%2C%20is%20located%20between%20Silkyara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20on%20the%20road%20proposed%20to%20connect%20Uttarkashi%20and%20Yamunotri.%20Work%20on%20the%204.5%20km%20tunnel%20has%20been%20mostly%20completed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFollowing%20a%20landslide%20on%20November%2012%2C%20the%20workers%20were%20trapped%20in%20the%20tunnel.%20The%20area%20they%20are%20stuck%20in%20is%20about%208.5%20metres%20high%20and%202%20km%20long.%20Fortunately%2C%20that%20part%20of%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%20has%20electricity%20and%20water%20supply.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20the%20past%2012%20days%2C%20the%20rescue%20operations%20ran%20into%20many%20difficulties%20owing%20to%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20region%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20soil.%20These%20factors%20led%20to%20frequent%20roadblocks%20and%20tardy%20progress%20in%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20owing%20to%20these%20challenges%20that%20rescue%20teams%20are%20still%20wary%20of%20providing%20an%20exact%20timeline%20to%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20operation.%20The%20workers%20may%20be%20brought%20out%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20hours%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20they%20have%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700715240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F8c2ns1j8_ambulance-uttarakhand-tunnel_625x300_23_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-in-last-phase-ambulances-on-standby-10-facts-4598279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20operation%20to%20rescue%2041%20workers%20trapped%20inside%20an%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20for%20the%20past%2012%20days%20is%20in%20its%20final%20phase.%20As%20of%20midnight%2C%20rescue%20teams%20had%20said%20that%20about%2010%20metres%20of%20debris%20separates%20them%20from%20the%20trapped%20workers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-in-last-phase-ambulances-on-standby-10-facts-4598279%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-in-last-phase-ambulances-on-standby-10-facts-4598279%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-in-last-phase-ambulances-on-standby-10-facts-4598279%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Good%20Day%20To%20Be%20A%20Dog%20records%20average%20ratings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700714834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105432938%2Cimgsize-181342.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fw