ic%20marks.%20Neighbourhood%20proximity%20holds%20the%20highest%20weightage%2C%20and%20many%20schools%20recommend%20using%20Google%20Maps%20for%20distance%20calculation%20due%20to%20potential%20inaccuracies%20in%20manual%20measurements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20criteria%20include%20considerations%20such%20as%20siblings%2C%20alumni%20connections%2C%20and%20certain%20schools%20even%20allocate%20points%20based%20on%20factors%20like%20being%20a%20firstborn%2C%20female%20child%2C%20or%20having%20a%20single%20parent.%20Schools%20retain%20the%20autonomy%20to%20define%20and%20assign%20marks%20for%20each%20criterion%20according%20to%20their%20discretion.%20Notably%2C%20no%20consideration%20is%20given%20to%20the%20parents'%20educational%20qualifications%2C%20occupation%2C%20or%20financial%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAge%20limits%20for%20admission%20are%203%20to%20under%204%20years%20for%20nursery%2C%204%20to%20under%205%20years%20for%20KG%2C%20and%205%20to%20under%206%20years%20for%20Class%20I.%20Admissions%20for%20the%2025%25%20quota%20reserved%20for%20economically%20weaker%20sections%2Fdisadvantaged%2Fchildren%20with%20special%20needs%20will%20be%20administered%20directly%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Education%2C%20with%20specific%20details%20to%20be%20released%20at%20a%20later%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EValid%20documents%20for%20proof%20of%20address%20include%3A%20Ration%20Card%20or%20Smart%20Card%20in%20the%20parents'%20names%20(mother%2Ffather%20with%20the%20child's%20name)%2C%20domicile%20certificate%20of%20the%20child%20or%20their%20parents%2C%20Voter%20ID%20Card%20(EPIC)%20of%20either%20parent%2C%20electricity%20bill%2C%20MTNL%20telephone%20bill%2C%20water%20bill%2C%20or%20passport%20in%20the%20name%20of%20either%20parent%20or%20the%20child%2C%20and%20Aadhaar%20card%20or%20UID%20card%20issued%20in%20the%20name%20of%20either%20parent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edudel.nic.in%2Fupload%2Fupload_2023_24%2F8873_8882_