o%20be%20one%20of%20the%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20after%20it%20attacked%20a%20music%20festival%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border%2C%20was%20found%20on%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShani%20Gabay's%20body%20was%20found%20under%20a%20burnt%20ambulance%20near%20the%20Supernova%20music%20festival%20site%20where%20she%20was%20working%20on%20October%207%2C%20reports%20said.%20When%20Hamas%20fired%20rockets%20at%20Israel%20and%20its%20gunmen%20attacked%20the%20site%2C%20several%20attendees%20hid%20under%20the%20ambulance%20that%20was%20later%20bombed%20by%20the%20gunmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20Shani%20is%20gone.%20Our%20hearts%20are%20broken%20into%20pieces.%20We%20are%20all%20crying%20and%20refuse%20to%20believe%2C%20how%20much%20we%20waited%20for%20a%20different%20ending.%20Forty-seven%20days%20of%20hope%20came%20to%20an%20end%20with%20receiving%20the%20bitter%20news%20this%20morning%20about%20the%20murder%20of%20Shani%20on%20October%207%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yokneam%20Mayor%20Simon%20Alfasi%20told%20The%20Jerusalem%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20family%2C%20Gabay%20had%20called%20her%20mother%20at%206%3A40%20am%20informing%20her%20about%20the%20rockets%20overhead%2C%20asking%20her%20what%20to%20do.%20Her%20mother%20advised%20her%20to%20get%20out%20of%20her%20car%20and%20find%20a%20place%20to%20hide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGabay%20reportedly%20hid%20in%20a%20field%20shelter%20near%20Kibbutz%20Alumim.%20Two%20of%20her%20friends%2C%20who%20survived%20the%20attack%2C%20said%20the%20gunmen%20threw%20grenades%20at%20the%20shelter%20so%20Gabay%20ran%20back%20to%20her%20car%20but%20was%20shot.%20Later%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20police%20command%20post%20to%20get%20medical%20help.%20She%20was%20not%20seen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20told%20to%20run%20but%20we%20don't%20know%20how%20well%20she%20could%20have%20run%20by%20that%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20brother%20told%20%C2%A0Israeli%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20heard%20nothing%20from%20her%2C%20Gabay's%20family%20set%20out%20to%20look%20for%20her%20at%20hospitals%20and%20medical%20centres%20where%20injured%20from%20the%20attack%20were%20taken.%20Her%20father%20headed%20to%20the%20sit%20of%20the%20party%20to%20find%20any%20clue%20to%20her%20whereabouts.%20Over%20the%20next%20five%20days%2C%20he%20turned%20over%20bodies%20lying%20in%20ditches%20and%20side%20of%20the%20roads%20to%20find%20her%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGabay%20was%20a%20recent%20law%20graduate%20who%20would%20have%20turned%2026%20next%20week%2C%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20festival%2C%20where%203%2C000%20people%20were%20reportedly%20partying%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20targets%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20whose%20gunmen%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20entered%20the%20site%20on%20motorbikes%2C%20trucks%20and%20ever%20gliders%2C%20seen%20flying%20over%20the%20festival%20in%20viral%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700713560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F8tvtpvg8_shani-gabay_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshani-gabay-israeli-woman-missing-after-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-music-fest-found-dead-4598318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20body%20of%20a%2025-year-old%20Israeli%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20assumed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20after%20it%20attacked%20a%20music%20festival%20near%20the%20Gaza%20border%2C%20was%20found%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshani-gabay-israeli-woman-missing-after-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-music-fest-found-dead-4598318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshani-gabay-israeli-woman-missing-after-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-musi