e%20circulation%20of%20known%20pathogens%2C%20including%20influenza%20and%20common%20bacterial%20infections%20that%20affect%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20capital%20has%20%26quot%3Bentered%20a%20high%20incidence%20season%20of%20respiratory%20infectious%20diseases%26quot%3B%2C%20Wang%20Quanyi%2C%20deputy%20director%20and%20chief%20epidemiological%20expert%20at%20the%20Beijing%20Center%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%2C%20told%20state-run%20outlet%20Beijing%20News%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20%26quot%3Bis%20currently%20showing%20a%20trend%20of%20multiple%20pathogens%20coexisting%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2021%2C%20media%20and%20public%20disease%20surveillance%20system%20ProMED%20reported%20clusters%20of%20undiagnosed%20pneumonia%20in%20children%20in%20northern%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20said%20it%20was%20unclear%20if%20ProMED's%20report%20was%20related%20to%20the%20authorities'%20press%20conference%20and%20that%20it%20was%20seeking%20clarification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20%26quot%3Bhas%20also%20requested%20additional%20information%20on%20recent%20trends%20in%20the%20circulation%20of%20known%20pathogens%2C%20including%20influenza%2C%20SARS-CoV-2%20(the%20virus%20that%20gives%20rise%20to%20Covid-19)%2C%20RSV%20affecting%20infants%20and%20Mycoplasma%20pneumoniae%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20degree%20of%20overcrowding%20in%20the%20health%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20it%20urged%20people%20to%20take%20preventative%20measures%2C%20including%20getting%20vaccinated%2C%20keeping%20distance%20from%20sick%20people%20and%20wearing%20masks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20capital%20is%20currently%20experiencing%20a%20cold%20snap%2C%20with%20temperatures%20expected%20to%20plummet%20to%20well%20below%20zero%20by%20Friday%2C%20state%20media%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20gave%20no%20indication%20of%20Ch