ously%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20more%20casualties%20in%20their%20ranks%20while%20closing%20in%20around%20the%20perpetrators%20who%20were%20hiding%20on%20a%20mountainside%20with%20natural%2C%20cave-like%20structures%20beneath%20a%20canopy%20of%20dense%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20PAFF%20militants%20deliberately%20showed%20up%20in%20residential%20areas%20of%20Rajouri%20recently%20to%20bait%20the%20security%20forces%20and%20draw%20them%20out%20on%20a%20manhunt%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20the%20hilly%20district%20without%20assessing%20the%20risks%20remains%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shot%20near%20the%20site%20of%20the%20shootout%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20shows%20two%20men%20in%20civvies%20accompanying%20a%20team%20of%20Army%20soldiers%20who%20are%20hauling%20a%20cot%20down%20a%20hillock%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20An%20unidentified%20body%2C%20purportedly%20one%20of%20the%20Army%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20the%20shootout%2C%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20laying%20motionless%20on%20the%20cot%20under%20a%20red%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20slain%20soldiers%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Captain%20MV%20Pranjal%20of%2063%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20and%20Captain%20Shubham%20Gupta%20and%20Havildar%20Majid%20Ahmad%2C%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20elite%209%20PARA%20unit.%20The%20identity%20of%20the%20fourth%20soldier%20was%20not%20immediately%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Army%20major%20and%20another%20soldier%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20shootout%20but%20their%20condition%20is%20reportedly%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20bodies%20of%20Captain%20Gupta%20and%20Havildar%20Majid%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Poonch%2C%20have%20been%20recovered.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20continuous%20firing%20by%20the%20heavily-armed%20militants%2C%20the%20bodies%20of%20Captain%20Pranjal%20and%20the%20unidentified%20soldier%20have%20not%20been%20retrieved%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPir%20Panjal%20a%20militancy%20epicentre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20Union%20territories%2C%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20region%2C%20which%20comprises%20twin%20districts%20of%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20Reasi%20district%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20new%20epicentre%20of%20militancy%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20militancy-related%20violence%20and%20local%20recruitment%20has%20gone%20down%20significantly%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20the%20focus%20of%20violence%20has%20seemingly%20shifted%20to%20Jammu%20which%20was%20a%20militancy-free%20region%20before%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20deadliest%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20civilians%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20Rajouri%20since%202019.%20Five%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Forces%20unit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fjammu%2Fencounter-underway-in-jks-rajouri-district-8592648%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Budhal%20area%20of%20Rajouri%20while%20an%20officer%20was%20injured%20in%20an%20IED%20explosion%20in%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20civilians%20including%20two%20children%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmilitants-shoot-dead-civilians-in-rajouri%2Farticle66327745.ece%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%20on%20the%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20eve%20this%20year%20in%20Dhangri%20area%20of%20Rajouri%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202022%2C%20five%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20predawn%20suicide%20attack%20on%20an%20Army%20camp%20in%20Rajouri%E2%80%