E%20emerged%20as%20the%20top%20wicket-taker%20in%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20bagging%2024%20scalps%20in%20just%207%20matches.%20His%20heroic%20performances%20with%20the%20ball%20took%20India%20as%20far%20as%20the%20final%20of%20the%20event.%20While%20entire%20India%20celebrated%20Shami's%20success%2C%20some%20bizarre%20accusations%20came%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20former%20player%20Hasan%20Raza%20accusing%20the%20Indian%20team%20of%20'cheating'.%20Raza%20suggested%20that%20Shami%20and%20Indian%20bowlers%20were%20given%20different%20balls%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20opponent%20team.%20Reflecting%20on%20the%20accusations%2C%20Shami%20was%20left%20scratching%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20pacer%20wasn't%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20playing%20XI%20for%20the%20first%20game.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20missed%20the%20first%204%20World%20Cup%20matches%20before%20being%20drafted%20into%20the%20team%20after%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20injured%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20hit%20the%20ground%20running%20with%20two%20fifers%20and%20a%204-wicket%20haul%20in%20the%20next%207%20matches%20he%20played.%20But%2C%20seeing%20some%20former%20Pakistan%20cricket%20stars'%20comments%2C%20Shami%20said%20that%20the%20people%20across%20the%20border%20couldn't%20digest%20his%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20pray%20to%20god%20that%2010%20bowlers%20come%20up%20with%20my%20kind%20of%20performance.%20I%20am%20not%20jealous%20of%20anyone.%20If%20you%20start%20enjoying%20the%20success%20of%20others%2C%20you%20will%20become%20a%20better%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20said%20in%20an%20with%20Puma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20hearing%20a%20lot%20since%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days.%20I%20was%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Playing%20XI%20in%20the%20initial%20matches.%20When%