20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fmissions%2Fpsyche-mission%2Fnasas-deep-space-optical-comm-demo-sends-receives-first-data%2F%5C%22%3ENASA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that's%2040%20times%20farther%20than%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20Earth%20and%20the%20moon%2C%C2%A0making%20it%20the%20longest%20demonstration%20of%20optical%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20Deep%20Space%20Optical%20Communications%20(DSOC)%20tool%20which%20was%20travelling%20onboard%20NASA's%20Psyche%20spacecraft.%20It%20set%20off%20on%20October%2013%20from%20the%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%20in%20Florida%20and%20it's%20since%20been%20successful%20in%20sending%20a%20laser-beamed%20message%20back%20to%20Earth.%20On%20November%2014.%20the%20Psyche%20spacecraft%20established%20a%20communication%20link%20with%20the%20Hale%20Telescope%20at%20the%20Palomar%20Observatory%20in%20California.%20DSOC's%20near-infrared%20photons%20took%20about%2050%20seconds%20to%20travel%20from%20Psyche%20to%20Earth%20during%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20successful%20establishment%20of%20the%20comms%20link%20is%20known%20as%20the%20'first%20light'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Achieving%20first%20light%20is%20one%20of%20many%20critical%20DSOC%20milestones%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20toward%20higher-data-rate%20communications%20capable%20of%20sending%20scientific%20information%2C%20high-definition%20imagery%2C%20and%20streaming%20video%20in%20support%20of%20humanity's%20next%20giant%20leap%2C''%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fmissions%2Fpsyche-mission%2Fnasas-deep-space-optical-comm-demo-sends-receives-first-data%2F%5C%22%3E%20said%20Trudy%20Kortes%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20is%20director%20of%20Technology%20Demonstrations%20at%20NASA%20Headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbi%20Biswas%2C%20project%20technologist%20for%20DSOC%20at%20NASA%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BReceiving%20first%20light%20is%20a%20tremendous%20achievement.%20The%20deep%20space%20laser%20photons%20from%20DSOC's%20flight%20transceiver%20aboard%20Psyche%20were%20successfully%20detected%20by%20ground%20equipment.%20We%20could%20also%20convey%20data%2C%20implying%20that%20we%20may%20interchange%20'bits%20of%20light'%20from%20and%20to%20deep%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20purpose%20of%20the%20Psyche%20spacecraft%20is%20to%20explore%20and%20study%20the%20unique%20metallic%20asteroid%20Psyche%2C%20providing%20insights%20into%20the%20history%20of%20planet%20formation%20and%20core%20dynamics.%20The%20experiment%20is%20planned%20to%20last%20two%20years%2C%20sending%20and%20receiving%20laser%20signals%20from%20increasingly%20distant%20locations%20on%20its%20way%20to%20its%20final%20destination.%C2%A0The%20spacecraft%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20asteroid%20in%202029%20and%20will%20then%20proceed%20to%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20administrator%20Bill%20Nelson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20''The%20Psyche%20mission%20could%20provide%20humanity%20with%20new%20information%20about%20planet%20formation%20while%20testing%20technology%20that%20can%20be%20used%20on%20future%20NASA%20missions.%20As%20Asteroid%20Autumn%20continues%2C%20so%20does%20NASA's%20commitment%20to%20exploring%20the%20unknown%20and%20inspiring%20the%20world%20through%20discovery.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20communications%20with%20craft%20in%20deep%20space%20are%20achieved%20through%20radio%20signals%2C%20sent%20and%20received%20from%20vast%20antennas%20on%20Earth.%20However%2C%20their%20bandwidth%20is%20limited.%20With%20this%20experiment%2C%20NASA%20ultimately%20hopes%20to%20use%20lasers%20to%20send%20information%20between%20Earth%20and%20spacecraft%20using%20light%20instead%20of%20radio%20waves.%C2%A0%20The%20system%20is%20capable%20of%20beaming%20information%2010%20to%20100%20times%20faster%20than%20current%20space%20communications%20equipment%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Once%20achieved%2C%20NASA%20would%20not%20only%20be%20able%20to%20aid%20human%20and%20robot%20missions%20but%20also%20send%20higher-resolution%20instruments%20into%20deep%20space%20for%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700707560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fk07kv7ag_nasas-psyche-spacecraft-_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhistoric-breakthrough-earth-receives-first-laser-message-from-16-million-km-from-deep-space-4598320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20experiment%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20Deep%20Space%20Optical%20Communications%20(DSOC)%20tool%20which%20was%20travelling%20onboard%20NASA's%20Psyche%20spacecraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhistoric-breakthrough-earth-receives-first-laser-message-from-16-million-km-from-deep-space-4598320%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhistoric-breakthrough-earth-receives-first-laser-message-from-16-million-km-from-deep-space-4598320%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhistoric-breakthrough-earth-receives-first-laser-message-from-16-million-km-from-deep-space-4598320%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mukesh%20Chhabra%3A%20Dunki%20is%20better%20than%203%20Idiots%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700707559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105429441%2Cimgsize-70692.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmukesh-chhabra-feels-shah-rukh-khans-dunki-is-100-times-better-than-aamir-khan-starrer-3-idiots%2Farticleshow%2F105429409.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi