alty-after-player-catches-ball-with-towel-watch-4597115%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sydney%20Sixers%20defeated%20Brisbane%20Heat%20by%20six%20wickets%20in%20their%20previous%20Women's%20Big%20Bash%20League%20match%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fteam-faces-5-run-penalty-after-player-catches-ball-with-towel-watch-4597115%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fteam-faces-5-run-penalty-after-player-catches-ball-with-towel-watch-4597115%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fteam-faces-5-run-penalty-after-player-catches-ball-with-towel-watch-4597115%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCricket%20Won%26quot%3B%3A%20After%20'Aishwarya'%20Row%2C%20Razzaq%20Now%20Takes%20Aim%20At%20Team%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abdul%20Razzaq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F95-abdul-razzaq-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbdul%20Razzaq%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20aim%20at%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20following%20their%20loss%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20against%20Australia%20and%20he%20said%20that%20India's%20defeat%20meant%20that%20'cricket%20won'.%20In%20a%20recent%20interaction%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20accuse%20India%20of%20using%20home%20conditions%20to%20their%20advantage%20and%20said%20that%20a%20win%20for%20India%20over%20Australia%20would%20have%20been%20'a%20sad%20moment%20for%20cricket'.%20Razzaq%20earlier%20courted%20controversy%20for%20his%20comment%20about%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20which%20contained%20a%20reference%20to%20Bollywood%20actress%20Aishwarya%20Rai.%20The%20former%20cricketer%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%20for%20his%20comment%20and%20later%2C%20he%20tendered%20an%20official%20apology%20for%20his%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAgar%20sahi%20baat%20kare%20toh%20aaj%20cricket%20jeeti%20hai.%20Aap%20conditions%20ko%20apni%20taraf%20utilise%20karke%2C%20ye%20kabhi%20bhi%20nahi%20aisa%20hota.%20Agar%20aaj%20India%20jeet%20jaati%20toh%20fir%20cricket%20jo%20hai%20naa%20vo%20India%20ki%20taraf%20ho%20jaati.%20Cricket%20ne%20bataya%20ki%20mai%20vo%20cricket%20hu%20jo%20brave%20hote%20hai%2C%20jo%20strong%20hote%20hai%20mentally%2C%20effort%20krte%20hai%2C%20jaan%20maarte%20hai%2C%20mai%20unke%20saath%20hu.%20Khushi%20iss%20cheej%20ki%20hai%20aaj%20ki%20agar%20India%20jeet%20jaati%20na%20to%20hume%20bahut%20jyada%20afsos%20hota%20iss%20sense%20mei%20ki%20vo%20conditions%20ko%20utilise%20kar%20rahi%20thi.%20Kuch%20na%20kuch%20toh%20hai%20conditions%20mei.%20Bilkul%20fair%20pitches%20honi%20chahiye%2C%20bilkul%20fair%20atmosphere%20hona%20chahiye%2C%20ki%20dono%20teams%20ke%20liye%20balance%20hona%20chahiye.%20Aaj%20bhi%20India%20ne%20advantage%20liya%2C%20agar%20Kohli%20100%20kar%20jaate%20toh%20India%20ye%20World%20Cup%20jeet%20jaati%3C%2Fem%3E%20(If%20I%20am%20being%20honest%2C%20cricket%20won.%20They%20were%20using%20the%20conditions%20to%20their%20advantage.%20Had%20India%20won%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20sad%20moment%20for%20cricket.%20Cricket%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20helps%20the%20team%20who%20are%20brave%20and%20mentally%20strong.%20If%20India%20would%20have%20won%2C%20I%20would%20have%20felt%20very%20bad.%20The%20pitches%20should%20be%20fair%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20should%20fair%20and%20there%20should%20be%20balance%20for%20both%20teams.%20India%20tried%20to%20take%20advantage%20even%20in%20the%20final%20and%20if%20Kohli%20scored%20another%20century%2C%20India%20would%20have%20once%20again%20won%20the%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20Razzaq%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfDXUeIp4qqc%5C%22%3EPakistani%20TV%20show%20'Hasna%20Mana%20