%2F2020%2F04%2F27%2F846438983%2Famazon-warehouse-safety-inadequate-n-y-attorney-general-s-office-says%5C%22%3Einadequate%20safety%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20exposed%20employees%20to%20risks%20of%20injury%20or%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Famazon-warehouse-profits-workers-culture%5C%22%3EA%20Look%20Inside%20an%20Amazon%20Warehouse%20%E2%80%93%20Where%20Profits%20Are%20Placed%20Ahead%20of%20Workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20tell%20us%20that%20Amazon%E2%80%99s%20performance%20monitoring%20system%20makes%20them%20feel%20%E2%80%9Cstressed%2C%20pressured%2C%20anxious%2C%20and%20untrusted%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20a%202023%20UNI%20Global%20Union%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6248340%2Famazon-injuries-survey-labor-osha%2F%5C%22%3Esurvey%20of%20Amazon%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20eight%20countries%2C%20including%20Amazon%E2%80%99s%20largest%20markets.%20Over%20half%20of%20the%202%2C000%20workers%20surveyed%20said%20Amazon%E2%80%99s%20monitoring%20systems%20have%20had%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20their%20physical%20(51%25)%20and%20mental%20health%20(57%25).%20The%20US%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osha.gov%2Fnews%2Fnewsreleases%2Fnational%2F02232023-0%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Occupational%20Safety%20and%20Health%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CAmazon%E2%80%99s%20work%20processes%20are%20designed%20for%20speed%2C%20not%20safety%2C%20and%20that%20these%20processes%20cause%20serious%20injuries%20to%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20US%20Senator%20Bernie%20Sanders%20has%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress%2Fbernie-sanders-announces-investigation-amazons-safety-record-rcna90223%5C%22%3Eabysmal%20safety%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20impact%20of%20Amazon%E2%80%99s%20practices%20is%20not%20confined%20to%20its%20warehouses%20in%20any%20particular%20country%3B%20the%20damage%20it%20causes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6248340%2Famazon-injuries-survey-labor-osha%2F%5C%22%3Eworkers%20spills%20across%20economic%20sectors%20and%20borders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20no%20exception.%20One%20worker%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20retaliation%2C%20told%20us%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pressure%20to%20work%20is%20so%20much%20that%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewe%20are%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20the%20washroom%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20we%20get%20stomachaches.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20answer%20our%20phones%20or%20speak%20to%20anyone%2C%20and%20if%20we%20get%20very%20tired%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20rest%20anywhere%E2%80%A6%20If%20we%20have%20not%20achieved%20our%20targets%2C%20they%20speak%20to%20us%20in%20an%20abusive%20language%20and%20force%20us%20to%20resign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20that%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20now%2C%20Amazon%20workers%20everywhere%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20struggle%20for%20justice%20and%20corporate%20accountability.%20With%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fgerman-union-verdi-calls-prime-day-strike-by-amazon-workers-2022-07-10%2F%5C%22%3Epersistent%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20organising%20and%20forming%20works%20councils%2C%20Amazon%20workers%20had%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funiglobalunion.org%2Fnews%2Farticle-title-goes-here-lorem-ipsum%2F%5C%22%3Eincrease%20their%20wages%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funiglobalunion.org%2Fnews%2Famazon-workers-win-india%2F%5C%22%3Eimprove%20working%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20push%20back%20against%20overwork%20and%20algorithmic%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20pandemic%20came.%20In%20response%2C%20workers%20across%20the%20globe%20rose%20up%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20h