%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20September%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20for%20a%20country%20to%20decide%20who%20represents%20them%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Li%20Qiang%20had%20represented%20them%20at%20the%20G20%20New%20Delhi%20Summit%20as%20well%2C%20so%20they%20chose%20to%20continue%20with%20that...%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaihshankar%20said%20during%20the%20G20%20closing%20presser%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EAM%20further%20said%20that%20India's%20G20%20presidency%20was%20Global%20South-centric%2C%20and%20it%20had%20brought%20development%20back%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20G20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20one%20point%2C%20I%20think%2C%20which%20all%20of%20us%20would%20have%20noted%20today%2C%20a%20very%20clear%20recognition%2C%20that%20India's%20G20%20presidency%20was%20Global%20South-centric%2C%20and%20it%20had%20brought%20development%20back%2C%20fair%2C%20square%2C%20and%20centre%20of%20the%20G20.%20Think%20this%20was%20a%20very%20widely%20voiced%20thought%20not%20just%20among%20the%20G20%20members%2C%20but%20also%20I%20would%20say%20among%20the%20international%20organisations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20that%20G20%20members%20welcomed%20the%20understanding%20reached%20on%20critical%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20relief%20material%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20a%20temporary%20pause%20in%20the%20fighting.%20The%20leaders%20conveyed%20a%20strong%20sentiment%20towards%20ensuring%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20agreed-upon%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BG20%20members%20on%20the%20whole%20welcome%20the%20understanding%20that%20has%20been%20reached%20on%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20relief%20material%20to%20Gaza%20and%20some%20pause%20in%20the%20fighting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20overall%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20sentiment%20expressed%20by%20the%20leaders%20to%20ensure%20implementation%20of%20the%20commitments%20that%20were%20agreed%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20briefing%20was%20also%20addressed%20by%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Finance%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20India's%20G20%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%20and%20MEA%20official%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20highlighted%20the%20G20%20finance%20track%20related%20issues%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Every%20one%20of%20the%20five%20main%20agenda%20points%20which%20had%20been%20discussed%20over%20the%20year%2C%20had%20been%20reiterated.%20They%20were%20welcomed...MDB%20reforms%2C%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20road%20map%20for%20crypto%20assets%2C%20climate%20finance%2C%20and%20financing%20of%20cities%20of%20tomorrow.%20On%20all%20these%20agendas%2C%20as%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Declaration%2C%20there%20was%20overwhelming%20appreciation%20and%20keenness%20to%20take%20it%20forward%20during%20the%20next%20presidency...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20MDBs%20are%20already%20exploring%20options%20of%20collaborating%20with%20each%20other%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20innovative%20finance.%20The%20international%20expert%20group's%20report%20has%20been%20welcomed.%20Many%20aspects%20of%20it%20are%20already%20set%20on%20course%2C%20the%20boards%20are%20taking%20it%20up%20for%20each%20of%20the%20banks..%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhereas%2C%20G20%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%20underlined%20that%20the%20number%20of%20things%20that%20were%20taken%20up%20by%20India%20are%20now%20all%20being%20carried%20forward%20by%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20we%20had%2022%20heads%20of%20government%20and%20all%20heads%20of%20international%20organisation%20participating%20in%20it.%20So%20it%20was%20a%20very%20well-attended%20virtual%20conference.%20Secondly%2C%20since%20G20%20works%20in%20contin