p%3ETo%20help%20combat%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20city%20is%20aiming%20to%20build%2040%2C000%20new%20affordable%20rental%20units%20by%202030%2C%20and%20the%20mayor%2C%20Olivia%20Chow%2C%20hopes%20to%20increase%20that%20number%20by%20more%20than%2020%2C000%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Ftoronto%2Fontario-housing-annual-summit-2023-1.6993867%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBC%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20of%20today%2C%20Ettinger%20said%20the%20listing%20she%20discovered%20is%20just%20another%20example%20of%20how%20severe%20the%20housing%20crisis%20is.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20paints%20a%20very%20grim%20picture%20of%20the%20affordability%20crisis%20that%20we're%20experiencing%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20nowhere%20near%20New%20York's%20level%20of%20unaffordability%20relative%20to%20income%2C%20but%20it's%20pretty%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frealtor-apartment-tenants-share-queen-bed-grim-affordable-housing-crisis-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700688076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e16e79c7d23cb3b9eae52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frealtor-apartment-tenants-share-queen-bed-grim-affordable-housing-crisis-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canadian%20realtor%20Anya%20Ettinger%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20people%20are%20having%20to%20turn%20to%20%26quot%3Bunconventional%26quot%3B%20setups%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Toronto's%20housing%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frealtor-apartment-tenants-share-queen-bed-grim-affordable-housing-crisis-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Terry%20Richardson%20sexually%20abused%20a%20model%20after%20Trump's%20modeling%20agency%20dismissed%20her%20concerns%20about%20him%2C%20lawsuit%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Terry%20Richardson%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e6a0722cf74a5739bcaeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221485%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhotographer%20Terry%20Richardson%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3ERaymond%20Hall%2FFilmMagic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETerry%20Richardson%20sexually%20abused%20a%20model%20on%20two%20separate%20occasions%20in%202004%2C%20a%20new%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump's%20modeling%20agency%20waved%20off%20her%20concerns%2C%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERichardson%20published%20photos%20of%20the%20alleged%20abuse%20in%20a%20book%20and%20gallery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESometime%20in%202004%2C%20Minerva%20Portillo%20had%20a%20meeting%20with%20Terry%20Richardson%20in%20his%20downtown%20Manhattan%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20fashion%20photographers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20going%20on%20to%20work%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Tom%20Ford%2C%20Vogue%2C%20Vanity%20Fair%2C%20and%20Yves%20Saint%20Laurent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%2C%2022%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20just%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20from%20Spain%20and%20was%20excited%20for%20the%20next%20phase%20in%20her%20modeling%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20appeared%20enthusiastic%20at%20the%20idea%20of%20working%20with%20Portillo%2C%20but%20she%20left%20the%20meeting%20feeling%20perturbed%2C%20according%20to%20a%20lawsuit%20she%20filed%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20their%20meeting%2C%20Mr.%20Richardson%20wore%20nothing%20but%20a%20robe.%20Ms.%20Portillo%20was%20disturbed%20by%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20lawyers%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BShe%20tried%20to%20keep%20the%20meeting%20professional%20and%20kept%20her%20distance%20from%20Mr.%20Richardson%20while%20they%20looked%20through%20her%20portfolio%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Portillo%20expressed%20her%20trepidation%20to%20her%20agents%20at%20Trump%20Model%20Management%20%E2%80%94%20the%20modeling%20agency%20founded%20in%201999%20by%20now-former-President%20Donald%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20and%20told%20them%20that%20Richardson%20had%20worn%20only%20a%20robe%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20waved%20away%20her%20distress%2C%20her%20suit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20Model%20Management%20dismissed%20her%20concerns%2C%20telling%20her%20that%20such%20behavior%20was%20commonplace%20and%20that%20given%20Mr.%20Richardson's%20prominence%20and%20influence%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20Ms.%20Portillo%20should%20overlook%20his%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agents%20booked%20a%20photoshoot%20with%20Richardson%20for%20that%20May%2C%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%20When%20she%20arrived%20at%20his%20studio%2C%20an%20employee%20offered%20a%20beverage%20that%20made%20her%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20dizzy%2C%20disoriented%2C%20and%20not%20fully%20in%20control%20of%20her%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20photoshoot%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20Richardson%20instructed%20her%20to%20remove%20her%20clothing%20before%20forcing%20her%20to%20perform%20oral%20sex%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20tried%20to%20push%20Mr.%20Richardson%20away%20and%20attempted%20to%20back%20away%20from%20him.%20But%20she%20was%20closely%20surrounded%20by%20Mr.%20Richardson's%20employees%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20cheering%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Richardson%20had%20his%20hand%20on%20her%20head%2C%20keeping%20her%20in%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20and%20his%20employees%20snapped%20photos%20while%20he%20sexually%20abused%20her%2C%20Portillo's%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20had%20another%20appointment%20with%20Richardson%20the%20next%20day%2C%20for%20a%20fashion%20brand%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20She%20%26quot%3Battempted%20to%20tell%20an%20agent%20at%20Trump%20Model%20Management%20about%20the%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20lawsuit%20says%2C%20but%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Binsisted%20that%20she%20proceed%20with%20the%20appointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%2C%20Richardson%2C%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20photography%20crew%20traveled%20in%20a%20van%20back%20to%20Manhattan%20from%20the%20shoot%20location.%20In%20the%20van%2C%20Richardson%20%26quot%3Bunbuckled%20his%20pants%2C%20grabbed%20her%20head%2C%20and%20forced%20it%20towards%20his%20penis%20without%20her%20consent%26quot%3B%20before%20commanding%20her%20to%20perform%20oral%20sex%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20also%20while%20his%20staff%20took%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20returned%20to%20Spain%20a%20week%20later%2C%20abandoning%20her%20modeling%20career%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERichardson%20included%20the%20photos%20in%20a%20book%20and%20gallery%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20has%20faced%20numerous%20sexual%20assault%20accusations%20since%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20was%20effectively%20ousted%20from%20the%20fashion%20industry%20in%202017%20amid%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement.%20An%20attorney%20for%20Richardson%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20Portillo's%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20had%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.es%2Fmoda%2Fnews%2Farticulos%2Fminerva-portillo-terry-richardson-modelo-historia-acoso-sexual-verdad%2F31964%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecounted%20her%20story%20in%202017%2C%20to%20Vogue%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20brought%20her%20new%20lawsuit%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20under%20the%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act%2C%20a%20New%20York%20law%20passed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement%20that%20created%20a%20one-year%20window%20permitting%20accusers%20to%20bring%20civil%20sexual%20misconduct%20lawsuits%20that%20would%20otherwise%20be%20barred%20by%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations.%20The%20window%20for%20new%20lawsuits%20closes%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Minerva%20Portillo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e6a5c22cf74a5739bcb3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222292%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMinerva%20Portillo%20at%20a%20Vogue%20Spain%20event.%3Cp%3EGabriel%20Maseda%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Richardson%2C%20corporate%20entities%20related%20to%20Trump%20Model%20Management%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffashion%2Fshortcuts%2F2017%2Fapr%2F11%2Ftrump-model-agency-closing-mother-jones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20stopped%20operating%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20named%20as%20defendants%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%20Attorneys%20representing%20those%20entities%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20does%20not%20identify%20the%20particular%20agents%20who%20represented%20Portillo%20and%20booked%20the%20meetings%20with%20Richardson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20to%20Ms.%20Portillo%20was%20foreseeable%20and%20preventable%2C%20because%20she%20had%20shared%20her%20concerns%20about%20working%20with%20Mr.%20Richardson%20with%20Trump%20Model%20Management%2C%26quot%3B%20Aleix%20Cuadrado%2C%20a%20Spain-based%20attorney%20representing%20Portillo%20in%20the%20case%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20published%20the%20photos%20allegedly%20depicting%20Richardson's%20sexual%20assault%20in%20a%20photo%20gallery%20and%20a%20book%2C%20and%20sold%20at%20least%20