-1235805330%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Texas%20and%20back%20to%20California%20after%204%20years.%20Now%20we%20live%20in%20a%20mobile%20home%20park%20by%20the%20beach.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20photo%20of%20dan%20and%20mary%20next%20to%20a%20photo%20of%20their%20mobile%20home%20in%20santa%20cruz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6557fc5822cf74a57399c79d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDan%20Otis%20and%20Mary%20Collins%20(left)%20moved%20from%20Coarsegold%2C%20California%20to%20Rosenberg%2C%20Texas%20in%202018.%20Four%20years%20later%20they%20moved%20back%20to%20California%20and%20now%20live%20in%20a%20mobile%20home%20in%20Santa%20Cruz%20(right).%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dan%20Otis%20and%20Mary%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDan%20Otis%20and%20Mary%20Collins%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Texas%20in%202018%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20couple%20loved%20the%20affordability%20and%20ease%20of%20Texas%2C%20but%20struggled%20with%20the%20weather%20and%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOtis%20and%20Collins%20moved%20back%20to%20California%20after%20four%20years%20in%20Texas%20and%20now%20live%20in%20Santa%20Cruz%2C%20California.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Dan%20Otis%2C%2075%2C%20and%20Mary%20Collins%2C%2074%2C%20a%20retired%20couple%20who%20moved%20from%20Coarsegold%2C%20California%2C%20to%20Rosenberg%2C%20Texas%2C%20in%202018%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20family.%20After%20four%20years%20in%20Texas%2C%20the%20couple%20moved%20back%20to%20California%20and%20now%20live%20in%20Santa%20Cruz.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20was%20born%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area.%20My%20wife%20grew%20up%20in%20Queens.%20She%20has%20a%20q