der%20than%20the%20female%20bat's%20vagina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20does%20a%20species%20reproduce%20when%20they%20have%20a%20square%20peg%20and%20round%20hole%20situation%3F%20That's%20what%20the%20scientists%20simply%20had%20to%20find%20out%2C%20Fasel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20scientific%20peep%20show%20and%20future%20bat%20porn%20box%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20full%20body%20photograph%20of%20serotine%20bat%20lying%20on%20its%20belly.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655789e336d588dc55d24d96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20researchers%20observed%20the%20serotine%20bat%20in%20the%20attic%20of%20a%20church%20and%20a%20bat%20rehabilitation%20center.%3Cp%3EOlivier%20Glaizot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESerotine%20bats%20are%20found%20all%20over%20Europe%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanimaldiversity.org%2Faccounts%2FEptesicus_serotinus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnimal%20Diversity%20Web%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20study%20focused%20on%20a%20population%20of%20bats%20living%20in%20the%20attic%20of%20a%20Dutch%20church%20and%20in%20a%20bat%20rehabilitation%20center%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20at%20the%20church%20and%20rehab%20center%20were%20observing%20the%20bats%20using%20cameras%20set%20up%20under%20a%20grid%20that%20the%20animals%20could%20climb%20on.%20Fasel%20and%20his%20team%20obtained%20the%20footage%20and%20scanned%20through%20it%20specifically%20for%20mating%20examples%2C%20and%20they%20weren't%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20observed%2097%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frare-video-seal-inflates-nose-like-ballon-in-mating-ritual-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emating%20rituals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Each%20time%2C%20instead%20of%20putting%20its%20penis%20inside%20a%20partner's%20vagina%2C%20the%20male%20bats%20used%20it%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20arm%2C%20to%20move%20the%20female%20bat's%20tail%20membrane%20out%20of%20the%20way%20for%20easy%20access%20to%20the%20vaginal%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20male%20bat%20held%20the%20female%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bextended%20embrace%26quot%3B.%20In%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fhow-to-increase-sex-drive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20impressive%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20went%20on%20for%2012.7%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FSXZgObDN-puACk8ZV.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20Fasel%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20researchers%20want%20to%20make%20an%20even%20more%20comprehensive%20viewing%20theater%20to%20observe%20the%20bats.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20can%20observe%20all%20sides%20of%20the%20bat's%20environment%20to%20try%20and%20understand%20how%20they%20reproduce%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20develop%20a%20bat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-porn-valley-hugh-hefner-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eporn%20box%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20will%20be%20like%20an%20aquarium%20with%20cameras%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Fasel%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbats-giant-penises-mate-without-penetrating-first-mammals-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700684323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6557998e22cf74a573995aec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbats-giant-penises-mate-without-penetrating-first-mammals-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%2