e-mental-health-care-doctor-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpertise%20of%20a%20psychologist%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20paediatrician%20and%20an%20ex-school%20principal%20to%20discern%20the%20types%20of%20toys%20that%20would%20be%20most%20beneficial%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20nearly%20a%20year%20of%20developing%20the%20concept%20and%20ensuring%20that%20all%20our%20toys%20meet%20the%20highest%20quality%20standards%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20launch%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20has%20a%20customer%20base%20of%20more%20than%20250%20subscribers%20with%20over%202%2C000%20downloads%20of%20the%20application%20per%20day.%20They%20also%20have%20collaborations%20with%2070%20toy%20companies%20where%20they%20source%20their%20toys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20these%20250%20subscribers%20is%20Rahul%20Bhauwala%20from%20Mumbai%20who%20rents%20toys%20for%20his%206-year-old.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20working%20professional%20and%20I%20hardly%20get%20any%20time%20to%20go%20out%20and%20spend%20hours%20looking%20for%20and%20buying%20toys.%20I%20could%20use%20that%20precious%20time%20to%20play%20with%20my%20child%20instead.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20love%20using%20The%20EleFant%20app.%20They%20have%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20toys%20which%20are%20categorised%20as%20per%20age.%20The%20products%20are%20very%20well-packaged%20and%20my%20son%20loved%20opening%20them%20as%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20present%20to%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20aim%20to%20establish%20a%20circular%20economy%20where%20toys%20are%20reused%20repeatedly.%20This%20not%20only%20cuts%20costs%20but%20also%20benefits%20the%20environment.%20Considering%20how%20quickly%20kids%20outgrow%20things%2C%20toys%20often%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPocket-friendly%20for%20parents%20and%20fun%20for%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20habit%20of%20reusing%20and%20thrifting%20might%20have%20started%20trending%20recently%2C%20if%20we%20look%20back%20to%20our%20childhood%2C%20sharing%20children%E2%80%99s%20belongings%20has%20always%20been%20part%20of%20our%20culture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20pass%20down%20our%20toys%20and%20clothes%20to%20our%3Cem%3E%20chachi%2C%20mami%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20(aunts)%20kids.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20nuclear%20family%20setup%2C%20this%20trend%20has%20declined.%20I%20think%20it%20was%20this%20practice%20that%20has%20made%20people%20place%20their%20trust%20in%20us%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20reaction%20of%20the%20people%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20were%20very%20delighted%20and%20showed%20encouragement.%20While%20they%20were%20a%20little%20sceptical%20of%20sanitation%20since%20these%20products%20will%20be%20reused%2C%20I%20explained%20that%20we%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F115268%2Fbaghuwar-village-madhya-pradesh-sanitation-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esanitation%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20every%20toy%20that%20reaches%20their%20kid%20is%20safe%20for%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-8-1700662925.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20offer%2014%20categories%20of%20toys%20that%20help%20in%20the%20cognitive%20development%20of%20children.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-8-1700662925.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-8-1700662925-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th