3Cem%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F169599016203ADSI-2021Chapter-2Suicides-ExcludingFarmerCauses.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENCRB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20data%3C%2Fem%3E%20revealed%20that%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C881%20persons%20involved%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202021.%20With%2037.3%20percent%2C%20Maharashtra%20accounted%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20farmer%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20impoverished%20farmers%20have%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20oyster%20pearls%20in%20the%20water-starved%20Marathwada%20to%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20recurring%20droughts%20and%20low%20crop%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20farmer%20is%20Sanjay%20Narsing%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20nine%20other%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20harvested%208%2C000%20pearls%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20pond%2C%20earning%20them%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229545%2Fagra-woman-entrepreneur-grow-oysters-pearl-farming-home-earn-lakhs-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoyster%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette