%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-IN)%20has%20been%20tasked%20to%20make%20Apple%20explain%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3Esecurity%20notifications%20on%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%E2%80%9D%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20this%20month%2C%20but%20can%20it%20follow%20through%20with%20due%20process%20and%20actually%20do%20its%20job%3F%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20is%20to%20provide%20response%20to%20computer%20emergencies%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%20It%20has%20never%20delivered%20on%20this%20promise%20and%20has%20become%20yet%20another%20government%20agency%20sleeping%20on%20its%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20notifications%20sent%20by%20Apple%20to%20several%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20politicians%2C%20journalists%20and%20others%20has%20raised%20concerns%20yet%20again%20of%20unregulated%20surveillance%20activities%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20agencies.%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20security%20notifications%20point%20towards%20state-sponsored%20actors%20and%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20argument%2C%20could%20mean%20any%20nation%20state%20including%20an%20enemy%20state%20out%20there%2C%20making%20it%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20computer%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20390px)%2085vw%2C%20390px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22272%5C%22%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Apple%20asking%20the%20firm%20to%20cooperate%20with%20CERT-IN%20and%20Apple%20has%20co-operated%20by%20bringing%20in%20its%20experts%20to%20work%20with%20CERT-IN.%20CERT-IN%20guidelines%20mandate%20that%20every%20organisation%20must%20report%20security%20incidents%20within%20six%20hours%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20Apple%20was%20reminded%20of%20this.%20Apple%20clearly%20has%20not%20followed%20this%2C%20violating%20some%20of%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECERT-IN%20similarly%20sent%20notices%20to%20WhatsApp%20in%202019%2C%20when%20WhatsApp%20alerted%20select%20individuals%20of%20being%20targeted%20by%20Pegasus.%20WhatsApp%20notified%20CERT-IN%20about%20the%20security%20issue%20in%20its%20systems%20without%20giving%20further%20details%20of%20people%20early%20into%20its%20incident%20response%2C%20even%20before%20it%20notified%20people%20who%20were%20affected.%20CERT-IN%20did%20not%20follow%20through%20on%20the%20issue%20until%20the%20scale%20of%20it%20was%20publicly%20disclosed%20by%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news-technology%2Fgovt-investigating-whether-china-linked-agencies-are-behind-apple-spyware-attack-9032714%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20investigation%20into%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20security%20notifications%20pointed%20out%20how%20CERT-IN%20is%20now%20investigating%20Chinese%20government-linked%20agencies%2C%20as%20the%20place%20of%20production%20of%20most%20iPhones%20is%20China.%20CERT-IN%20is%20now%20investigating%20which%20nation%20state%20actor%20could%20be%20behind%20these%20attacks%2C%20while%20the%20minister%20for%20electronics%20and%20information%20technology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcentre-reacts-to-oppositions-hacking-claim-says-compulsive-critics-want-to-distract-indian-people%2Farticleshow%2F104850753.cms%5C%22%3Edenied%20it%20could%20be%20Indian%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rubbished%20the%20opposition%20for%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20past%20actions%20show%20us%20that%20these%20notices%20that%20it%20issues%20to%20private%20companies%20have%20never%20been%20translated%20into%20any%20meaningful%20regulatory%20actions.%20Neither%20did%20CERT-IN%20follow%20through%20with%20WhatsApp%20about%20Pegasus%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20carry%20out%20an%20independent%20investigation%20which%20most%20cyber%20security%20agencies%20in%20different%20countries%20carried%20out.%20As%20a%20regulatory%20body%20responsible%20for%20cyber%20security%2C%20CERT-IN%20has%20never%20investigated%20any%20data%20breaches%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20provided%20any%20actual%20incident%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Seizing%20Devices%20Needs%20Due%20Process.%20So%20Does%20Remote%20Accessing%20Via%20Spyware%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-guidelines-rules-procedures%5C%22%3ESeizing%20Devices%20Needs%20Due%20Process.%20So%20Does%20Remote%20Accessing%20Via%20Spyware%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bureaucratic%20body%20under%20MeitY%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20clearly%20not%20an%20independent%20institution%20and%20has%20no%20history%20of%20actually%20conducting%20serious%20forensic%20audits.%20The%20organisational%20capacity%20to%20even%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20necessary%20for%20state-sponsored%20attacks%20is%20probably%20not%20available%20to%20CERT-IN.%20Most%20of%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20is%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20privately%20regulated%20cybersecurity%20industry.%20CERT-IN%20decides%20who%20can%20conduct%20cybersecurity%20audits%20by%20empanelling%20private%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20digital%20evidence%20perspective%2C%20no%20private%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20forensics%20are%20considered%20valid%20unless%20that%20organisation%20is%20empanelled%20by%20CERT-IN.%20This%20gives%20CERT-IN%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20more%20power%20to%20reject%20any%20forensic%20evidence%20just%20because%20the%20organisations%20%E2%80%98can%E2%80%99t%20be%20trusted%E2%80%99.%20Even%20if%20Apple%20provides%20evidence%20there%20were%20indeed%20state-sponsored%20attacks%2C%20with%20no%20actual%20conclusive%20proofs%20attributing%20exact%20actors%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20are%20likely%20to%20reject%20it%20or%20deflect%20the%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20long%20pending%20demand%20for%20CERT-IN%20to%20actually%20conduct%20forensic%20investigations%20of%20cyber%20incidents%20and%20to%20publish%20its%20findings.%20The%20only%20major%20reports%20that%20are%20published%20by%20CERT-IN%20are%20its%20annual%20reports%20with%20details%20of%20its%20activities%20like%20training%20and%20workshops%20it%20has%20conducted.%20As%20a%20cybersecurity%20regulator%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20as%20bad%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20regulators%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20no%20interest%20in%20seriously%20regulating%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20sake%20of%20argument%2C%20if%20it%20were%20indeed%20Chinese%20actors%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20targeting%20the%20Indian%20opposition%20and%20journalists%2C%20even%20then%20CERT-IN%20has%20no%20capacity%20to%20respond%20to%20this.%20The%20National%20Critical%20Information%20Infrastructure%20Protection%20Centre%20(NCIIPC)%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20the%20National%20Technical%20Research%20Organisation%20(NTRO)%2C%20has%20relatively%20more%20experience%20in%20tackling%20nation%20state%20actors%20targeting%20our%20critical%20infrastructure.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20cybersecurity%2C%20NCIIPC%20still%20responds%20to%20threats%20and%20provides%20incident%20response%2C%20which%20CERT-IN%20has%20largely%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20CERT-IN%20is%20basically%20a%20regulatory%20organisation%20responsible%20for%20directing%20the%20industry%20to%20adopt%20cybersecurity%20practices%2C%20NCIIPC%20is%20more%20of%20a%20hands-on%20organisation%20that%20has%20in-house%20capacity%20to%20handle%20threats.%20If%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20really%20serious%20about%20addressing%20nation%20state%20actors%20targeting%20Indians%20and%20is%20concerned%20with%20the%20safety%20of%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20and%20others%2C%20it%20would%20comprehensively%20address%20this%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Apple%20Is%20Not%20the%20First%20Tech%20Company%20To%20Allege%20Government%20Role%20in%20Misuse%20of%20Spyware%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fapple-tech-company-allege-government-role-spyware-misuse%5C%22%3EApple%20Is%20Not%20the%20First%20Tech%20Company%20To%20Allege%20Government%20Role%20in%20Misuse%20of%20Spyware%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20more%20transparency%20on%20how%20its%20security%20apparatus%20and%20its%20regulators%20operate.%20This%20is%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20by%20itself%20and%20with%20the%20parliament%20and%20its%20committees%20unable%20to%20function%20under%20the%20current%20political%20climate%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20wait%20for%20political%20change.%20One%20could%20only%20hope%20that%20actually%20happens%20and%20the%20situation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20worse%20with%20the%20usage%20of%20state%20surveillance%20against%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20this%20and%20want%20more%20answers%20from%20Apple%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20revealed%20in%20India.%20If%20one%20is%20looking%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20this%20and%20want%20Apple%20to%20provide%20more%20details%2C%20they%20should%20legally%20proceed%20against%20Apple%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Any%20litigation%20around%20this%20in%20India%20is%20unlikely%20to%20result%20in%20any%20positive%20response%20from%20any%20of%20the%20actors.%20Apple%20sued%20the%20NSO%20Group%20in%20the%20US%20for%20targeting%20its%20users%20and%20to%20curb%20abuse%20of%20nation%20state%20actors.%20If%20Apple%20is%20really%20serious%20about%20the%20privacy%20of%20its%20users%2C%20it%20will%20respond%20positively%20and%20give%20further%20details%2C%20but%20may%20be%20unlikely%20to%20do%20so%20in%20India%20with%20pressure%20from%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700659812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F05194313%2FIMG_4672.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhy-cert-ins-investigation-into-apple-security-notifications-is-going-nowhere%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bureaucratic%20body%20under%20MeitY%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20clearly%20not%20an%20independent%20institution%20and%20has%20no%20history%20of%20actually%20conducting%20serious%20forensic%20audits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhy-cert-ins-investigation-into-apple-security-notifications-is-going-nowhere%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20Sikh%20separatist%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil%2C%20reports%20FT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700659651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fmisc%2F2023-11%2F22%2Ffull%2F20230925191L.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-foiled-plot-to-kill-sikh-separatist-pannun-on-american-soil-reports-ft-123112200889_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20mu