assengers-123112200940_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdgca-puts-rs-10-lakh-penalty-on-air-india-for-not-compensating-passengers-123112200940_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%2C%20Women%2C%20Corruption%20and%20Jobs%3A%20Comparing%20Congress%2C%20BJP's%20Rajasthan%20Manifestos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22172044%2FThe-Wire-85.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20Rajasthan%20heads%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20November%2025%2C%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20released%20their%20poll%20documents%20highlighting%20social%20justice%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20and%20empowerment%2C%20assistance%20to%20farmers%2C%20action%20on%20paper%20leaks%2C%20reduced%20prices%20of%20LPG%20cylinders%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20releasing%20the%20manifesto%2C%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20said%20that%20the%20poll%20manifesto%20is%20a%20roadmap%20for%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20other%20parties%2C%20the%20manifesto%20is%20just%20a%20formality%2C%20but%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20a%20roadmap%20of%20development.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20respected%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20BJP%20is%20committed%20to%20fulfil%20these%20announcements.%20The%20history%20of%20BJP%20is%20witness%20to%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20Party%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20five%20things%20in%20five%20years.%20First%20%E2%80%93%20corruption.%20Second%20%E2%80%93%20insult%20to%20sisters%2C%20daughters%20and%20mothers.%20Third%20%E2%80%93%20contempt%20of%20farmers.%20Fourth%20%E2%80%93%20atrocities%20against%20the%20poor.%20Fifth%20%E2%80%93%20playing%20with%20the%20future%20of%20youth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20said%20that%20it%20has%20already%20fulfilled%20over%2090%25%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20its%202018%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20fulfilled%2096%25%20of%20our%20manifesto%20because%20our%20motto%20as%20Kharge%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20say%20is%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20promises%20and%20if%20you%20do%2C%20then%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20fulfilled%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20while%20releasing%20the%20manifesto%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20corruption%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20lack%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20and%20paper%20leaks%20major%20poll%20issues%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20buck%20the%20trend%20of%20revolving%20door%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20and%20make%20a%20comeback%20riding%20on%20its%20flagship%20schemes%20for%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20how%20the%20poll%20documents%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20compares%20on%20key%20issues%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromises%20to%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20immediate%20priorities%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20bring%20a%20law%20to%20implement%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20following%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%2C%20interest-free%20loans%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20all%20farmers%20from%20cooperative%20banks%2C%20withdraw%20pending%20cases%20against%20farmers%20in%20connection%20with%20their%20participation%20in%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%20additional%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20to%20farmers%20under%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%2C%20free%20education%20to%20farmers%E2%80%99%20children%2C%20an%20additional%20bonus%20of%20Rs%202%2C700%20per%20quintal%20over%20the%20MSP%20on%20wheat%2C%20along%20with%20providing%20MSP%20on%20jowar%20and%20bajra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadda%20while%20releasing%20the%20manifesto%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20snatching%20lands%20from%2019%2C400%20farmers%2C%20and%20promised%20to%20compensate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGehlot%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20said%20that%20a%20commission%20headed%20by%20a%20high%20court%20judge%20will%20be%20constituted%20to%20look%20into%20cases%20where%20farmers%E2%80%99%20lands%20have%20been%20seized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%20(ERCP)%20has%20become%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20seeks%20to%20address%20water%20scarcity%20in%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20by%20diverting%20water%20from%20the%20Chambal%20basin.%20The%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmodi-failed-to-fulfil-promise-of-granting-national-project-status-to-eastern-rajasthan-canal-project-cong%2F1853935%2F%5C%22%3Enot%20giving%20national%20status%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20project%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-responsible-for-stalling-east-rajasthan-canal-project-rathore-123101700003_1.html%5C%22%3E%20stalling%20the%20project.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20introduce%20a%20Detailed%20Plan%20for%20the%20Staggered%20Implementation%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%20(ERCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20too%20has%20promised%20to%20implement%20the%20project%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20made%20the%20alleged%20corruption%20by%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20one%20of%20its%20main%20poll%20planks%2C%20has%20promised%20to%20constitute%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20look%20into%20exam%20paper%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20form%20another%20SIT%20to%20look%20into%20fertiliser%2C%20mid-day%20meal%2C%20mining%2C%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20and%20other%20alleged%20scams%20and%20bring%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20White%20Paper%20listing%20all%20instances%20of%20corruption%20by%20the%20Gehlot%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%20leaks%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20implement%20%E2%80%9Cmeasures%20and%20stringent%20punishments%20to%20curb%20incidents%20of%20paper%20leaks%20for%20competitive%20exams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGehlot%20said%20that%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20make%20an%20issue%20out%20of%20exam%20paper%20leaks%2C%20nowhere%20in%20the%20country%20is%20there%20a%20more%20stringent%20law%20than%20Rajasthan%20on%20paper%20leaks%20which%20includes%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20charge%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20install%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20public%20places%2C%20security%20guards%20in%20every%20village%20and%20urban%20wards%2C%20and%20reduce%20the%20average%20time%20taken%20to%20investigate%20sexual%20harassment%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F02152935%2FScreen-Shot-2020-07-02-at-3.25.07-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%