has%20promised%20to%20provide%20them%20at%20Rs%20450%20to%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20in%20its%20manifesto%20has%20said%20that%20while%20the%20state%20government%20at%20present%20provides%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20they%20will%20decrease%20it%20further%20to%20Rs%20400%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20it%20will%20extend%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20affordable%20LPG%20cylinder%20scheme%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20to%20families%20under%20the%20NFSA%20(National%20Food%20Security%20Act)%20and%20BPL%20(Below%20Poverty%20Line)%20categories%E2%80%9D%20and%20commit%20to%20further%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20gas%20cylinders%20to%20Rs%20400%20for%20Ujjwala%2C%20NFSA%2C%20and%20BPL%20families%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouth%20and%20employment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%2010%20lakh%20employment%20opportunities%20including%204%20lakh%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%202.5%20lakh%20government%20jobs%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20a%20new%20scheme%20for%20the%20recruitment%20of%20youngsters%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%2C%20gradually%20merging%20with%20government%20vacancies.%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20start%20a%20toll-free%20call%20centre%20and%20an%20e-Employment%20Exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-556745%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnemployed%20youth%20protesting%20against%20irregularities%20which%20took%20place%20in%20government%20exams%20under%20Rajasthan%20Ekikrat%20Berozgaar%20Mahasangh.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FUpen%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%202.5%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20youth%20it%20has%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Rajasthan%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Rajasthan%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20modelled%20on%20AIIMS%20and%20IITs%20%E2%80%93%20in%20each%20division%2C%20among%20several%20other%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20rural%20jobs%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20increase%20employment%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20150%20days%20of%20guaranteed%20work%20from%20125%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20free%20English%20medium%20education%20to%20girls%20and%20boys%20and%20to%20bring%20an%20education%20guarantee%20law%20in%20the%20state%20and%20provide%20free%20education%20till%20class%2012%20as%20opposed%20to%20class%208%20under%20RTE%20(Right%20to%20Education).%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20provide%20first-year%20students%20of%20government%20colleges%20with%20a%20free%20laptop%2Ftablet%20upon%20admission%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20promised%20free%20education%20from%20KG%20to%20PG%20to%20poor%20families%20and%20annual%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20for%20students%20of%20poor%20families%20to%20purchase%20school%20bags%2C%20books%20and%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20Free%20Scooty%20Scheme%2C%20arrangements%20will%20be%20made%20to%20give%20free%20scooty%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students%20after%20passing%20class%2012th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20already%20operates%20a%20scheme%20in%20the%20state%20to%20provide%20scooters%20to%20students%20under%20the%20Kalibai%20Bhil%20Medhavi%20Chhatra%20Scooty%20Yojana%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20double%20the%20coverage%20under%20its%20flagship%20health%20insurance%20scheme-the%20Mukhyamantri%20Nishulk%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana%20from%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%20it%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20increase%20the%20facilities%20under%20free%20OPD%2FIPD%20in%20government%20medical%20institutions%20at%20the%20district%20and%20block%20level%20and%20include%20IVF%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20recognise%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20profound%20emotional%20and%20social%20challenges%20faced%20by%20couples%20deprived%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20parenthood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20has%20promised%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20through%20the%20Bhamashah%20Health%20Infrastructure%20Mission%20and%20appointment%20of%2015%2C000%20doctors%20and%2020%2C000%20paramedical%20staff.%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20350%20Jan%20Aushadi%20Kendras%20and%20at%20least%20one%20medical%20college%20in%20each%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20census%2C%20hate%20speech%20and%20Anti-Bharat%20cells%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20%E2%80%9Cto%20accurately%20determine%20population%20and%20allocate%20benefits%20for%20informed%20decisions%20