2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20promised%20to%20create%2010%20lakh%20employment%20opportunities%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20with%20four%20lakh%20in%20the%20government%20sectors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20manifesto%20also%20addresses%20various%20facets%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20economic%20participation.%20The%20former%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20often.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20has%20said%20it%20will%20install%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20all%20public%20places%2C%20and%20that%20security%20guards%20will%20be%20appointed%20in%20every%20village%20and%20urban%20ward%20of%20Rajasthan.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20planned%20to%20reduce%20the%20average%20investigation%20time%20in%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%20for%20speedy%20justice%20in%20the%20state.%20Free%20coupons%20will%20also%20be%20provided%20for%20free%20travel%20for%20women%20in%20state-owned%20buses%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESmartphones%20with%20free%20internet%20will%20also%20be%20given%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20families%20covered%20under%20Mukgyamantri%20Nishulak%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20also%20plans%20to%20target%20women%20farmers%20to%20encourage%20homestead%20gardens%20and%20horticulture%2C%20recognising%20their%20crucial%20role%20in%20agriculture.%20Women%2C%20it%20has%20promised%2C%20will%20also%20get%2033%25%20reservation%20in%20cooperative%20institutions%2C%20championing%20gender%20equality%20in%20cooperative%20governance.%20Women%20representatives%20will%20be%20empowered%20with%20essential%20skills%2C%20including%20financial%20literacy%2C%20and%20recognise%20and%20incentivise%20best-performing%20women-led%20Gram%20Panchayats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Grameen%20Aajeevika%20Vikas%20Parishad%20or%20women-centric%20financial%20institution%20will%20give%20subsidised%3C%2Fspan%3E%20loans%20to%20women%20through%20Cluster%20Level%20Federations%20(CLFs)%20and%20benefit%2030%20lakh%20households%20through%20agriculture%20and%20livestock%20programmes%2C%20Congress%20has%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20will%20also%20introduce%20a%20leadership%20course%20to%20promote%20the%20emergence%20of%20next-generation%20leaders%20among%20SHG%20women%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20spoke%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20set%20a%20target%20to%20increase%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20police%20force%20to%2033%25%20of%20the%20total%20police%20strength%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20survey%20and%20minorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20will%20also%20conduct%20a%20census%20or%20survey%20based%20on%20caste%20to%20accurately%20determine%20population%20and%20allocate%20benefits%20for%20informed%20decisions%20on%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20this%20exercise%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20government%20will%20undertake%20to%20provide%20reservations%20as%20per%20their%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%20also%20talks%20about%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20communities.%20If%20the%20party%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20it%20says%20it%20will%20establish%20an%20equal%20opportunities%20commission%20to%20ensure%20equal%20opportunities%20and%20fair%20representation%20for%20them.%20Adding%20to%20this%2C%20the%20party%20will%20modify%20the%20percentage%20of%20reservation%20for%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20actual%20population%20to%20be%20enumerated%20in%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResearch%20centres%2C%20training%20facilities%2C%20and%20museums%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20Udaipur%20will%20be%20set%20up%20to%20nurture%20tribal%20youth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20promised%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20under%20the%20Mukhyamantri%20Nishulk%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana.%20Recently%20the%20Congress%20Government%20in%20Rajasthan%20increased%20the%20medical%20cover%20under%20the%20Chiranjeevi%20Health%20Scheme%20from%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20annually%20per%20family.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20will%20also%20bring%20an%20education%20guarantee%20law%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20planned%20to%20uplift%20the%20underprivileged%20in%20rural%20areas%20by%20guaranteeing%20150%20days%20of%20employment%20annually%2C%20currently%20125%20days.%20Similar%20to%20the%20Kisan%20Credit%20Card%20Scheme%2C%20the%20government%20will%20implement%20a%20%E2%80%9CVyapari%20Credit%20Card%20Scheme%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20will%20withdraw%20pending%20cases%20against%20farmers%20related%20to%20their%20participation%20in%20protests%20and%20ensure%20their%20rights%20are%20safeguarded%2C%20it%20said.%20Farmers%20will%20get%20three-phase%20electricity%20support%20for%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20from%20November%20to%20March%20each%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYouth%20will%20get%20more%20participation%20in%20leadership%20positions%20in%20government%20bodies.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20legislative%20fellowship%2C%20which%20will%20be%20similar%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20fellowship%2C%20giving%20youth%20leaders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20MLAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20ministers%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700653707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22171632%2FScreenshot-2023-11-22-at-5.16.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht