rently%2C%20they%20are%20also%20liable%20for%20encouraging%20recruitment%2C%E2%80%9D%20DGP%20Swain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20take%20action%20against%20those%20who%20hide%20behind%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20to%20provoke%20people.%20We%20will%20not%20tolerate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20appointed%20DGP%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20struck%20down%20the%20charges%20against%20journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%20under%20Sections%2018%20(terror%20conspiracy)%20and%20121%20(waging%20war%20against%20the%20country)%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA).%20The%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fafter-nearly-2-years-jk-hc-grants-bail-to-kashmir-walla-editor-fahad-shah%5C%22%3Egranted%20him%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20anti-terror%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20(SIA)%20had%20filed%20the%20case%20under%20various%20Sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20Foreign%20Contributions%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%2C%20after%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Findias-honour-not-its-incorporeal-property-says-jk-and-ladakh-hc-in-fahad-shah-order%2F%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20received%20%E2%80%9Csource%20information%E2%80%9D%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EKashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Srinagar-based%20news%20outlet%20run%20by%20Shah%2C%20had%20published%20an%20article%20which%20was%20part%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20operation%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbreak%20up%20the%20Indian%20Union%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csecession%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20from%20India%20and%20its%20consequent%20accession%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20and%20Aala%20Fazili%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Kashmir%20scholar%20who%20had%20authored%20the%20piece%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20shackles%20of%20slavery%20will%20break%E2%80%99%2C%20were%20booked%20and%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%E2%80%99s%20elite%20counter-terrorism%20wing%2C%20DGP%20Swain%20was%20leading%20the%20SIA%20when%20the%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20April%204%2C%202022%20(FIR%20No%3A%2001%2F2022)%20at%20the%20CIJ%20police%20station%20in%20Jammu%2C%20and%20Aala%20and%20Shah%20were%20booked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20charge-sheet%2C%20the%20elite%20agency%2C%20which%20has%20overarching%20powers%20to%20take%20over%20militancy%20cases%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20article%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterror%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20hatched%20by%20Pakistan%20to%20%E2%80%9Cincite%20violence%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20had%20led%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdisturbance%20in%20public%20order%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAala%20and%20Shah%20were%20accused%20of%20breach%20of%20peace%2C%20terrorism%20and%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20and%20senior%20advocate%20P.N.%20Raina%20rejected%20the%20charges%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20SIA%20had%20%E2%80%9Cmysteriously%E2%80%9D%20discovered%20the%20article%2011%20years%20after%20its%20publication%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20violence%2C%20breach%20of%20peace%20or%20any%20terror%20attack%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20article%20called%20for%20secession%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20from%20India%20and%20also%20accused%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20committing%20genocide%20of%20Kashmiris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20evidence%20of%20material%20damage%20caused%20to%20life%20or%20property%20by%20the%20purported%20write-up%2C%20which%20the%20prosecution%20sought%20to%20define%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98terrorist%20act%E2%80%99%20under%20Section%2015%20(1)%20(a)%20(ii)%20of%20the%20UAPA%2C%20the%20bench%20didn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20that%20the%20controversial%20article%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattack%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9Cact%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20argument%20is%20accepted%2C%20it%20would%20literally%20turn%20criminal%20law%20on%20its%20head.%20It%20would%20mean%20that%20any%20criticism%20of%20the%20central%20government%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20terrorist%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Mohan%20Lal%20and%20Atul%20Sreedharan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20none%20of%20the%20six%20prosecution%20witnesses%20examined%20so%20far%20in%20the%20trial%20have%20testified%20that%20there%20was%20any%20breach%20of%20peace%20or%20attack%20on%20security%20forces%20due%20to%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20court%20linked%20the%20write-up%20to%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20Shah%2C%20who%20will%20now%20face%20trial%20under%20Section%2013%20(abetting%20unlawful%20activities)%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20FCRA%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20framed%20the%20charges%20against%20Aala%20and%20Shah%20in%20March%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20has%20been%20booked%20in%20three%20other%20cases%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20preventive%20detention%20under%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA)%20earlier%20this%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20PSA%20proceedings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffahad-shah-public-safety-act-jammu-kashmir-high-court%5C%22%3Ewere%20also%20quashed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIA%2C%20which%20probed%20the%20case%20against%20%3