ankar%20was%20about%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20de-escalation%20in%20tensions%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20due%20to%20the%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20G20%20virtual%20meet%20and%20India%20announcing%20the%20resumption%20of%20e-visas%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20of%20all%20it%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20G20%20meeting.%20What%20had%20happened%20was%20we%20had%20temporarily%20suspended%20visa%20issuance%20because%20the%20situation%20in%20Canada%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20our%20diplomats%2C%20frankly%20to%20go%20to%20office%20and%20do%20the%20necessary%20work%20for%20processing%20visas.%20As%20the%20situation%20there%20has%20become%20more%20secure%20or%20relatively%20improved%2C%20we%20have%20found%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20visa%20services%20to%20progressively%20resume.%20The%20physical%20visas%20had%20started%20in%20many%20categories.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20we%20had%20said%20that%20we%20will%20look%20at%20e-visas%20next.%20So%20it%20was%20a%20logical%20consequence%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2021%2C%20India%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-visa-suspension%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520India%2520temporarily%2520suspended%2Ckilling%2520of%2520a%2520Sikh%2520activist.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20visa%20services%2C%20citing%20alleged%20%E2%80%98security%20threats%E2%80%99%20against%20diplomatic%20staff.%20Indian%20officials%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20safe%20for%20Indian%20diplomats%20to%20process%20visas%20in%20missions%20in%20Canada%2C%20signalling%20that%20Ottawa%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20its%20concerns%20was%20inadequate.%20India%20had%20also%20suspended%20e-visa%20services%20for%20Canadians%20despite%20the%20processing%20taking%20place%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csp