%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERukhsaar%20is%20a%20contestant%20on%20MasterChef%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20losing%20hope.%20There%20will%20come%20a%20day%20when%20you%20will%20be%20successful%20in%20whatever%20you%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20like%20a%20proverbial%20phoenix%2C%20Rukhsaar%20rose%20in%20September%202021%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Working%20out%20of%20the%20annexe%20of%20her%20house%2C%20in%20a%2010%20by%2010%20square%20feet%20room%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20two%20currently%20sells%20frozen%20products%20like%20chicken%20popcorn%2C%20crispy%20chicken%20strips%2C%20breaded%20chicken%20nuggets%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekalari%20%3C%2Fem%3Echeese%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20children%2C%20and%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Ekeema%20samosas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Turkish%20%3Cem%3Eadana%20kebabs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20chicken%20spring%20rolls%20for%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFocused%20on%20quality%2C%20she%20makes%20only%20one%20batch%20per%20week%20to%20ensure%20freshness.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20freeze%20the%20batch%20in%20our%20blast%20freezer.%20After%20it%E2%80%99s%20frozen%2C%20we%20pack%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20handmade%20and%20no%20machinery%20is%20used%20in%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20employs%20six%20people%20and%20gets%20about%20600%20to%20700%20orders%20per%20month%2C%20she%20informs.%20While%20her%20initial%20focus%20was%20just%20on%20online%20sales%2C%20the%20demand%20led%20her%20to%20sell%20her%20products%20in%20departmental%20stores%20in%20Srinagar%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20focus%20on%20keeping%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290986%2Fhemapriya-natesan-sathumaavu-traditional-powder-for-babies-no-sugar-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20clean%3C%2Fa%3E%20leads%20to%20a%20problem%20of%20storage%20as%