sed.%20Some%20videos%20got%20over%20a%20thousand%20views.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrainstorming%20with%20her%20younger%20brother%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echange%20strategies%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20these%20videos%20were%20not%20working.%20The%20shopping%20website%20Meesho%E2%80%99s%20hauls%20were%20trending%20then%2C%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20try%20that.%20The%20twist%2C%20she%20tried%2C%20was%20some%20over-the-top%20dancing%20and%20acting%20in%20the%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20very%20dedicated%20to%20this%20project.%20I%20put%20in%20as%20much%20effort%20and%20took%20it%20as%20seriously%20as%20I%20would%20my%20UPSC%20classes.%20So%20when%20nothing%20worked%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20some%20weird%20acting%20which%20people%20might%20find%20%E2%80%98cringe%E2%80%99.%20I%20was%20helpless.%20It%20was%20a%20do%20or%20die%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20videos%20finally%20grabbed%20eyeballs%2C%20but%20the%20publicity%20was%20mostly%20negative.%20Nancy%20was%20body%20shamed%20and%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20hate.%20Rather%20matter-of-factly%2C%20she%20says%20but%20%E2%80%98that%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20clicked%E2%80%99.%20The%20online%20trolls%20called%20her%20%E2%80%98skinny%E2%80%99%20and%20were%20brutal%20to%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nancy%20showed%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20tougher%20than%20them.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20the%20negative%20comments%20affect%20her%2C%20and%20worked%20steadfastly%20towards%20her%20purpose%20which%20was%20to%20help%20her%20mom%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20started%20working%20in%20a%20factory%20after%20we%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%20My%20father%20refused%20to%20support%20us%20financially%2